---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import instagram from '../images/icons/instagram.svg';
import facebook from '../images/icons/facebook.svg';
import logoTucont from '../images/tucont.svg';
---

<footer>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between">
            <!-- Coluna da logo (esquerda) -->
            <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-8 md:mb-3">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <Image src={logoTucont} alt="Mascote TuCont" width="300" class="mr-3" />
                    
                </div>
                <p class="mt-4 text-white">
                    A maior transformação do mercado de contabilidade nacional, unindo tecnologia e expertise humana para o sucesso do seu negócio.
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex space-x-4 mt-6">
                    <a href="https://web.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61560717810719&_rdc=1&_rdr#" target="_blank" class="p-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 from-20% to-orange-600 to-80%">
                        <Image src={facebook} alt="Facebook" width={24} height={24} />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tucont.contabilidade" target="_blank" class="p-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 from-20% to-orange-600 to-80%">
                        <Image src={instagram} alt="Instagram" width={24} height={24} />
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Grupo de 3 colunas alinhadas à direita -->
            <div class="flex gap-8 md:gap-10">
                <!-- Coluna Soluções -->
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 from-10% via-amber-300 via-40% to-orange-500 to-90% soft-neon-text text-lg font-bold mb-3">SOLUÇÕES</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Avenida Legal</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Avenida de Negócios</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Jornada Empresarial</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Marketplace</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Coluna Empresa -->
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 from-10% via-amber-300 via-40% to-orange-500 to-90% soft-neon-text text-lg font-bold mb-3">EMPRESA</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Sobre</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Blog</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Carreiras</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Contato</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Coluna Agentes -->
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 from-10% via-amber-300 via-40% to-orange-500 to-90% soft-neon-text text-lg font-bold mb-3">AGENTES</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="https://rouvbymulgc.typeform.com/to/OSIekGSL?typeform-source=www.tucont.com.br" target="_blank" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Seja um Agente</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Modelo de Negócio</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Treinamentos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-white hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors text-sm">Histórias de Sucesso</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rodapé inferior -->
        <div class="mt-0 pt-0">
            <div class="h-[1px] w-full mb-6" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%, rgba(255,145,0,0.5) 50%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%);"></div>
            <p class="text-white text-sm text-left">
                Tucont Contabilidade, somos uma DNVB - Digital Native Vertical Brand, empresa humanizada, que desde o nascimento é digital.<br>
                Nossa Plataforma utiliza Tecnologia Proprietária, Educação e práticas Corporativas, BPO Financeiro e de Contabilidade, para facilitar e participar da sua Jornada Empreendedora.<br>
                De empreendedores para empreendedores, destrave o empreendedorismo!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
<style>
    /* Efeitos de gradiente e hover */
    .soft-neon-text {
        text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(255, 145, 0, 0.4), 
                     0 0 8px rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.3);
    }
    
    /* Remove completamente o sublinhado */
    a, a:hover {
        text-decoration: none !important;
    }
    
    .hover\:text-amber-300:hover {
        color: #fbbf24;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    /* Responsividade */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .flex-col {
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        .gap-8 {
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .flex > div {
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .text-4xl {
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 2.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>